name: Duck vs Seagulls
description:
You, a righteous duck, should keep the cleanliness of the beach. Kill the pooping seagulls!

Controls

ActionKeyMove LeftA, ←Move RightD, →JumpW, ↑AttackMouse Left
  • Avoid seagulls poop
  • When you kill a seagull, double jump is refreshed and attack cooldown is largely reduced

My max height reached is 4566.

Leave your screenshot down in the comment if you can beat me 😉
